                  watchdog_enable PROC
;;;10974  //-----------------------------------------------
;;;10975  void watchdog_enable (void) 
009c96  4959              LDR      r1,|L2.40444|
;;;10976  {
;;;10977  LPC_WDT->WDTC=2000000;
009c98  05c8              LSLS     r0,r1,#23
009c9a  6041              STR      r1,[r0,#4]
;;;10978  LPC_WDT->WDCLKSEL=0;
009c9c  2100              MOVS     r1,#0
009c9e  6101              STR      r1,[r0,#0x10]
;;;10979  LPC_WDT->WDMOD=3;
009ca0  2103              MOVS     r1,#3
009ca2  7001              STRB     r1,[r0,#0]
;;;10980  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0xaa;
009ca4  21aa              MOVS     r1,#0xaa
009ca6  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;10981  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0x55;
009ca8  2155              MOVS     r1,#0x55
009caa  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;10982  }
009cac  4770              BX       lr
;;;10983  
                          ENDP

                  watchdog_reset PROC
;;;10984  //-----------------------------------------------
;;;10985  void watchdog_reset (void) 
009cae  21aa              MOVS     r1,#0xaa
;;;10986  {
;;;10987  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0xaa;
009cb0  0748              LSLS     r0,r1,#29
009cb2  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;10988  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0x55;
009cb4  2155              MOVS     r1,#0x55
009cb6  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;10989  }
009cb8  4770              BX       lr
;;;10990  
                          ENDP

                  SysTick_Handler PROC
;;;10996  //***********************************************
;;;10997  void SysTick_Handler (void) 	 /* SysTick Interrupt Handler (1ms)    */
009cba  e92d41f0          PUSH     {r4-r8,lr}
;;;10998  {
;;;10999  //sys_plazma++;
;;;11000  b2000Hz=1;
009cbe  4c4e              LDR      r4,|L2.40440|
009cc0  2601              MOVS     r6,#1
009cc2  3c80              SUBS     r4,r4,#0x80
;;;11001  
;;;11002  if(bTPS)
;;;11003  	{
;;;11004  	LPC_GPIO1->FIODIR|=(1UL<<26);
009cc4  484e              LDR      r0,|L2.40448|
009cc6  7326              STRB     r6,[r4,#0xc]          ;11000
009cc8  7de1              LDRB     r1,[r4,#0x17]         ;11002  ; bTPS
009cca  b139              CBZ      r1,|L2.40156|
009ccc  6a01              LDR      r1,[r0,#0x20]
009cce  f0416180          ORR      r1,r1,#0x4000000
009cd2  6201              STR      r1,[r0,#0x20]
;;;11005  	LPC_GPIO1->FIOPIN^=(1UL<<26);
009cd4  6b41              LDR      r1,[r0,#0x34]
009cd6  f0816180          EOR      r1,r1,#0x4000000
009cda  6341              STR      r1,[r0,#0x34]
                  |L2.40156|
;;;11006  	}
;;;11007  
;;;11008  if(++t0cnt4>=2)
009cdc  f8b41042          LDRH     r1,[r4,#0x42]  ; t0cnt4
009ce0  1c49              ADDS     r1,r1,#1
009ce2  b209              SXTH     r1,r1
009ce4  f8a41042          STRH     r1,[r4,#0x42]

009cea  db7e              BLT      |L2.40426|
;;;11009  	{
;;;11010  t0cnt4=0;
